        {
            "title": "淨虧損擴大至119.5億人民幣 萬科仍未能靠深圳輸血走出困境",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 萬科企業股份有限公司上半年淨虧損擴大，凸顯出這家開發商即使有了深圳市的財政援助也還持續面臨挑戰。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至6月30日的六個月，萬科錄得淨虧損119.5億元人民幣，去年同期淨虧損則為98.5億元人民幣。這一數字也接近萬科上個月預警區間的上限。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國持久的房地產危機繼續對萬科造成沉重打擊，百強房企7月銷售進一步惡化，當月70個大中城市新房均價環比創出九個月最大跌幅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管萬科第一大股東深鐵集團加大了資金支持力度，但房地產市場疲弱的大環境仍給其業績造成了額外壓力。萬科預計公司在經營上「仍面臨階段性壓力」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「萬科最大股東深圳地鐵的財務支持不太可能顯著緩解該開發商的流動性壓力或改善其前景，」 彭博行業研究分析師Kristy Hung和Patrick Wong在周一的報告中寫道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China Vanke’s Loss Widens to $1.7 Billion Despite Support</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B7%A8%E8%99%A7%E6%90%8D%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%B3119-5%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3-%E8%90%AC%E7%A7%91%E4%BB%8D%E6%9C%AA%E8%83%BD%E9%9D%A0%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E8%BC%B8%E8%A1%80%E8%B5%B0%E5%87%BA%E5%9B%B0%E5%A2%83-134153052.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-22 22:10:47",
